title: [1508521049] Best British Restaurant: The Result - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title. 

Gordon Ramsay reveals which british restaurant will go through to the next round of the competition.
